features: Package included: 1pcs Brush Wall Plate.Port: Single.Run your cables cleanly and neatly through the wall.
Suitable for home,office,commercial and industrial buildings for Computer, HDTV, Stereo and Audio, home theater system and others.
Brush design,organize and protect low voltage cable when passing through the wall, keep a clean, tidy, and professional look for your outlets.
Perfect for pre-made leads directly out of the wall cavity, allows the cables entering the wall cavity space and running behind your walls to exit the wall and connect to your devices.
Large aperture port works great with VGA, HDMI,Coaxial cables, multimedia, all standard AV audio video cables, speaker wires, network cables and other types of cables.
